<para>Implementing APIs can call this method in each frame to retrieve the current state for the gamepad, as computed by <ref refid="classhelios_1_1ext_1_1glfw_1_1input_1_1GLFWInputAdapter_1af65a6a8e99aac0f6867b6456d0849f9a" kindref="member">updateGamepadState()</ref>. This method guarantees that for a given gamepadId, a single GamepadState object is reused across calls, avoiding re-instantiation overhead.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>gamepadId</parametername>
